OL,3,CSewage burst prompts no swim warning
OL,4,Cas temperatures soar
OL,6,FA burst sewage line in Fareham has
OL,7,Fprompted a warning for people not to
OL,8,Fswim between Hill Head and Lee on the
OL,9,FSolent.
OL,11,FIt comes as people flock to beaches
OL,12,Famid soaring temperatures.
OL,14,FSouthern Water says it was alerted to
OL,15,Fthe leak on Tuesday. It says it has
OL,16,Fstopped the flow of sewage and is
OL,17,Fcarrying out work to fix the problem.
