OL,3,CSewage burst prompts no swim warning
OL,4,Cas temperatures soar
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We received
OL,7,Freports of a leaking sewer in the
OL,8,FSalterns Road area of Hill Head on the
OL,9,Fevening of Tuesday 9 July 2025, and
OL,10,Fattended immediately to prevent any
OL,11,Fimpact to the local environment.
OL,13,F"We temporarily stopped flows through
OL,14,Fthe problem pipe and used tankers to
OL,15,Fensure customers could continue to use
OL,16,Ftheir toilets, sinks and showers,
OL,17,Fwhile repairs have been carried out.
OL,19,F"This work is ongoing, with traffic
OL,20,Fmanagement in place. We apologise for
OL,21,Fany disruption caused."
