OL,3,CSewage burst prompts no swim warning
OL,4,Cas temperatures soar
OL,6,FThe water company is working with the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency on the
OL,8,Fenvironmental impacts.
OL,10,F"In close liaison with the EA, we are
OL,11,Fcarrying out detailed modelling of any
OL,12,Fpotential impacts on bathing water
OL,13,Fquality nearby, but in the meantime,
OL,14,Fthe EA has issued a precautionary
OL,15,Fbathing water advisory for the area
OL,16,Fand Fareham Borough Council has chosen
OL,17,Fto advise against bathing between Hill
OL,18,FHead and Lee on the Solent."
